  "title": "3 Months Engineering Inspector | Training Provided | Diploma Holder",
  "description": "<ul><li><strong>Role: First Article Inspector</strong></li><li><strong>Manufacturing Firm</strong></li><li><strong>Contract: 3-Months </strong><em><strong>(May have extensions based on project needs)</strong></em></li><li><strong>Working Hours: 8.30am - 5pm</strong></li><li><strong>Working Days: Monday - Friday</strong></li><li><strong>Basic Salary: $ 2300 - $ 2400</strong></li><li><strong>Working Location: 10 minutes walking from Pioneer MRT, Singapore</strong></li></ul><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Perform First Article Inspection and prepare First Article Inspection Reports (FAIR).</li><li>Submit FAIR at customer portal for approval.</li><li>Review internal inspection reports.</li><li>Review supplier FAIR and communicate with supplier for first article issues.</li><li>Perform administrative tasks such as document preparation and collection.</li><li>Perform other related duties as assigned.</li></ul><p><br /><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><u><em><strong>Diploma in mechanical or electrical engineering.</strong></em></u></li><li><u><em><strong>Training provided.</strong></em></u></li><li>Ability to read and comprehend mechanical drawings, technical specifications and product certifications.</li><li>Good working knowledge of inspection technique.</li><li>Hands-on knowledge on basic measuring tools such as caliper.</li><li>Basic Microsoft Office skills.</li><li>Previous experience in FAIR preparation is preferred.</li></ul><p><br />#SCR-carson-cheong</p><p></p><p>⭕ Cheong Kar Chun ⭕ Team Manager ⭕ R1980386</p><p>⭕ The Supreme HR Advisory ⭕ 14C7279</p><p></p>",
